                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Editor’s Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>—No official record of this conversation has been found. The principal subject
                    covered was the discussion of Swedish requisitioning of shipping which was
                    expected to take place at a forthcoming meeting of the United Maritime
                    Authority.</p>
            </div>
